Low malt sweetness and toast, cereal-like or other pale malt attributes should be present in ﬂavor and aroma at low to medium-low levels.', 'Chill haze should not be present', 'Hop aroma and ﬂavor should be medium-low to medium, with attributes typical of hops of any origin present but not dominant. 
