Low to medium-low malt aroma and flavor may be present', 'Low to very high degree of cloudiness is typical of these beers. Starch, yeast, hop, protein and/or other compounds contribute to a wide range of hazy appearance within this category.', 'Medium-high to very high hop aroma and flavor are present, with attributes typical of hops from any origin. 
Low to medium-low malt aroma and flavor may be present', 'Medium-low to medium-high. Perceived silky or full mouthfeel may contribute to overall flavor profile.');
