Medium levels of roasted malt, caramel and chocolate aromas and flavors should be present.', 'Chill haze is acceptable at low temperatures', 'Medium-low to medium-high 
Medium levels of roasted malt, caramel and chocolate aromas and flavors should be present.', 'Medium');
