Low to high malt aroma and flavor may be present', 'Low to very high degree of cloudiness is typical of these beers. Starch, yeast, hop, protein and/or other compounds contribute to a wide range of hazy appearance within this category.', 'High to very high hop aroma and flavor are present, with attributes typical of hops from any origin. 
